{"_id":"1pFoPKZbqGue8hfO","name":"Puppet","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The creature has no will of its own and must be directed by another mind. In consequence, it never surrenders or flees and will fight until destroyed.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2RsIqNmhzsx9vw6I","name":"Flying","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Using wings or similar, this creature can fly. Treat this as normal movement, but ignoring barriers that can be flown over at the game master's discretion. This creature cannot be engaged in melee combat whilst flying unless it chooses to attack, in which case it can be targeted.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4rg88jEJkvDJq2yr","name":"Ethereal","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This creature does not exist in the material plane. It can only be harmed by magic and magical weapons, and can pass through solid barriers such as doors and walls with ease.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"56fsf7S8NIppsAj2","name":"Poisonous","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This creature carries a poison or can inject a venom. If it successfully hits a target, the victim must test their luck. If they fail, the victim is poisoned, and loses [[/roll 1d6]] stamina at the start of the next [[/roll 1d3]] rounds. Poison or venom effects from the same source are not cumulative, although of course the creature can still inflict its normal damage when it hits.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9zIPNt2rdySokleu","name":"Regenerating","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The being is able to recover damage. Every round the being regains [[/roll 1d6]] stamina, up to a maximum of its starting value.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FOVCFt6tZfXWVBEK","name":"Spell caster","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The being is able to cast spells. The games master should feel free to assign the creature spells that reflect its power. It uses stamina to cast spells and requires an incantation skill check.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NJDwGhfTMjpd2eTv","name":"Brittle","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This creature is susceptible to impact damage. If maces, clubs or hammers attack them successfully, the damage is rolled twice and the higher value is applied.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UHb3vwM1JEJWJ7fl","name":"Formless","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The body of this creature has no real form, so it may slide under doors, squeeze through narrow spaces etc. as if it were a thick, viscous liquid.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YOeq0X3kQBWDsJdw","name":"Dissolve","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This being is able to dissolve matter. Any time it is successfully struck the attacker must test their luck. On a fail, their weapon is destroyed.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mYFyEyjPytD6nZiQ","name":"Tracking","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The creature is excellent at tracking other creatures by scent or another sense. Treat its adventuring skill at three times the normal level for tests involving tracking.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"v0qPMiXi02rlF9YG","name":"Flame","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The being has a flame attack that they can use once a round that ignores armour.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"viEhV1k2WBxXnAHV","name":"Intelligent","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"flags":{}}
